  </ul>

  <h2>Our Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> No hidden charges. No conflicts of interest. We tell you exactly what you pay and exactly why we recommend what we do.</li>
    <li><strong>Long-Term Thinking:</strong> We are not in the business of day-trading recommendations that generate brokerage. We are in the business of helping you build wealth over 10, 20, and 30 years.</li>
    <li><strong>Inclusion:</strong> Investing is not just for the wealthy. We have designed our products, minimums, and technology to serve India's aspiring middle class — the largest and fastest-growing investing demographic in the world.</li>
    <li><strong>Responsibility:</strong> We are deeply aware of the trust clients place in us. Every recommendation, every platform feature, every interaction is designed with the client's best interest as the primary measure of success.</li>
  </ul>

